reviews.review_text: Exceptional Recording Great to hear a quality recording of the best show I ever attended !!!

I love this I love the Starlight Theater. Listening to it this morning I remember every show they played here.
As far as quality it's outstanding. 
35 years later and I can remember clear as day where I was sitting when Jerry started Nobody's Fault. As everyone that ever saw these guys knows during Drums and space we would all huddle up and smoke during this time of the show. A very good friend had come to this tour with Many Many Many pounds of outstanding bud and is probably why I recall this so well. 
You know that look you get when you spark up something so nice , everybody looks to where it is coming from.  We were giving locals big fattys to enjoy.

Please everyone stay safe wear your masks.
